Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.39,0:24:19.85,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}状況は非科学的に
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.06,0:24:23.73,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}感情のモンタージュ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.94,0:24:26.44,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}誰が誰を呼んでる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.73,0:24:32.36,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}振り向けば　逃げてく視線　感じる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.61,0:24:34.91,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}気のせいじゃつれないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.95,0:24:39.99,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}アンテナは才能って言うでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.50,0:24:43.87,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}だってだって　知りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.12,0:24:45.63,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}君は違うの？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.71,0:24:52.38,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}青春の温度差　今のうち　正してあげるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.38,0:24:56.85,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}明日解決するなら　今でもよくない？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.97,0:25:02.60,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}君のミステリー　解いてみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.68,0:25:07.23,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}少年の秘密めいた背中探せ
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.40,0:25:10.94,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}今日も君はファンタジー
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.03,0:25:14.74,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}惹けれてゆくよ　ずるい
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.78,0:25:20.54,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}膨らんだ好奇心　トリックはないのに
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.58,0:25:24.79,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}気になるよ　興味深い
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.91,0:25:27.38,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}どうして
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.39,0:24:19.85,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}状况完全不科学
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.06,0:24:23.73,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}感情如拼贴画般交织
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.94,0:24:26.44,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}是谁在将谁呼唤
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.73,0:24:32.36,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}回头时感觉到你逃避的视线
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.61,0:24:34.91,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}说这是错觉未免无情
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.95,0:24:39.99,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}直觉该称为才能才对
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.50,0:24:43.87,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}因为我想了解你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.12,0:24:45.63,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}难道你并非如此？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.71,0:24:52.38,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}现在就为你纠正青春的温差
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.38,0:24:56.85,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}既然明天能解决 不如趁现在搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.97,0:25:02.60,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我想要解开你的悬疑
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.68,0:25:07.23,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}探寻少年神秘的背影
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.40,0:25:10.94,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}今天的你也如同幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.03,0:25:14.74,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}狡猾地吸引着我不断沉迷
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.78,0:25:20.54,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}膨胀的好奇中分明不含心机
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.58,0:25:24.79,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}令人在意 耐人寻味
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.91,0:25:27.38,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}这究竟是为什么
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,staff,NTP,0,0,0,,==========STORY==========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.85,0:00:04.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们闲不闲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.36,0:00:10.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想成为神山市抢答王吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.28,0:00:14.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,区区预选赛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.86,0:00:15.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可要突破啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.12,0:00:23.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问答预选赛7！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.59,0:02:02.89,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1500,300)\blur3\pos(1395,918)}傍晚便成骸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.89,0:02:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一问
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:10.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金刚石就是钻石 绿柱石就是祖母绿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.56,0:02:13.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是对的 还是错的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.12,0:02:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一问大概就这水准了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:26.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答案是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:34.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.55,0:02:40.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我告诉你 谁才是真正的数据库
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.68,0:02:44.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人数越来越少了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:47.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这会是预选赛的最后一个问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 第七问
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:54.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「迟钝」的语源是英语「dull」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:54.23,Default,NTP,0,600,0,,{\fs53}darui
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.73,0:02:56.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是对的还是错的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.61,0:02:59.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是哪个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.45,0:03:02.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉像是语源 不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.99,0:03:04.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么看 摩耶花？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.83,0:03:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得是对还是错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.45,0:03:09.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对的…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:10.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答案是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.21,0:03:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用卖关子了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.05,0:03:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,错的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.55,0:03:19.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预选结束
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.55,0:03:23.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜答对的同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:26.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决赛将在这边的台子上进行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:28.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 请上台
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.64,0:03:30.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:36.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福部 你打扮得挺有趣的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:37.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}这是第一位决赛选手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}请报上姓名和班级
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.40,0:03:39.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这人谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.03,0:03:41.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你完全没注意到我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.32,0:03:46.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我光顾着答题了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:49.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:51.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 谷同学 围棋部怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.04,0:03:52.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}不好意思 我有点紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:53.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,围棋部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.88,0:03:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}那么 继续介绍第二位决赛选手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出了件有趣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.71,0:04:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要听听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:03.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 下面是第三位决赛选手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:05.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:06.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位选手头上顶着土星呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请报上你的班级和姓名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.73,0:04:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是古典部的福部里志
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:21.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是古典部的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.90,0:04:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 还有叫古典部的社团啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:27.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个学校里奇怪的社团不少嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.62,0:04:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 这是个奇怪的社团
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.54,0:04:35.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为连活动目的都是个问号
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:37.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.54,0:04:41.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为知道要制作文集 所以就做了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果做得还挺不错的 花了很大力气的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确花了很大力气 在数量方面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:55.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文集里揭示了KANYA祭的重大秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.52,0:04:58.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦！那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:01.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,KANYA祭这个名字的由来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.78,0:05:04.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神山高中文化祭 简称KANYA祭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.53,0:05:06.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是这么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古典部把这个谜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彻底揭开了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.04,0:05:17.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那由来是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.17,0:05:19.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:24.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就请大家去买吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.26,0:05:26.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要200日元
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.51,0:05:30.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就能得到神山高中文化祭45年来的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:32.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文集「冰菓」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:36.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于特别教学楼四楼 地理准备室绝赞发售中！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:44.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,推销成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:47.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优胜什么的已经无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:50.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:55.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.79,0:05:59.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,田名边学长说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以让其他社团代售
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:08.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是我想去找入须学姐商量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.80,0:06:09.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却走不到那里…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛 原因倒是猜得到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:13.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下头疼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:18.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里志的宣传挺有趣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宣传…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.44,0:06:27.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 我记得墙报部会发行号外
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:30.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去问问他们能不能帮古典部写篇报道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.78,0:06:33.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是忙碌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:43.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnWenQuanYi Micro Hei\c&H1A282C&\3c&HB8D9DD&\pos(954,162)}墙报部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:43.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnMingLiU\fs45\c&H1F3538&\3c&HCFEBEE&\pos(943.5,526.5)\b1}欢迎爆料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.13,0:06:43.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.30,0:06:45.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:48.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 远垣内学长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能帮古典部写篇报道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:06:59.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不太明白你的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.98,0:07:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:08.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想拜托你在墙报部的报道里为古典部宣传一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:14.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 我已经不是部员了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.87,0:07:16.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经高三 所以退休了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:18.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 能帮我介绍一下后辈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:26.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那倒是可以 不过我觉得没什么用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.59,0:07:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们每两小时就要发一份号外
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:32.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日程事先就决定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:34.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没法刊发…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:36.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没说没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.31,0:07:40.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二天中午之后版面应该会有余地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是KANYA祭有50多个社团参加
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.23,0:07:47.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会优先报道那些值得关注的社团
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.36,0:07:49.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说可能有些失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:53.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我记得古典部只发行文集吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 文集的内容…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.91,0:07:59.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个社团的内容都是认真准备的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:02.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是有能吸引大家的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.33,0:08:04.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是可以拜托他们帮你写
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:07.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话题…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:09.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:12.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉占用了你的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是发生了什么有趣的事 就再来一趟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:18.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们说不定能帮得上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.89,0:08:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱琉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 华穗同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:29.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:32.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十文字伯伯之后还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.53,0:08:34.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经全好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.11,0:08:37.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来你好像闷闷不乐啊 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.70,0:08:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了一些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:46.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就进来 我帮你占卜一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:49.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是这么厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:53.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 就用塔罗牌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.76,0:08:57.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:08:59.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:04.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱琉 我记得你喜欢这种吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnFZLiBian-S02\b0\fs60\c&H4A545A&\3c&HEAF1F6&\pos(613.5,295.5)}占卜研究会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnFZLiBian-S02\b0\fs60\c&H4A545A&\3c&HEAF1F6&\pos(667.5,498)}已失去命运之轮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnFZLiBian-S02\b0\fs60\c&H4A545A&\3c&HEAF1F6&\pos(1281,729)}十文字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:14.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:18.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,占卜研只有我一个人 所以我时常离开
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.28,0:09:20.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出去一会儿再回来之后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:23.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命运之轮这张塔罗牌就不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:26.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而现场则留下了这张卡片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.17,0:09:30.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十文字…为什么会写着华穗同学的姓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.38,0:09:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 究竟为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.22,0:09:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丢失的那张牌找到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.34,0:09:38.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留在现场的还有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.89,0:09:40.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnFZLiBian-S02\b0\fs60\c&H4A545A&\3c&H7EE9F4&\pos(1032,718.5)}文化祭过后定当归还。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.01,0:09:40.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我觉得应该会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个古怪的小偷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.69,0:09:52.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后再给你看一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:55.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnFZZhunYuan-M02\fs52.5\c&H3295DC&\3c&HCDEFEE&\b1\pos(930,786)}带你漫步KANYA{\c&H616FD7&}祭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.19,0:09:55.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这本小册子有什么特别的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.45,0:09:58.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内容和发下来的那本一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:00.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟那张卡放在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:06.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翻开在参加社团一句话评论的最后一页
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:16.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是有什么意义呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:17.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要命运之轮好好还回来就满意了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.43,0:10:26.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 终于进入高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.98,0:10:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清水同学 后藤同学各5分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.56,0:10:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而谷同学 福部同学各6分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:34.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们离优胜都只有一分之遥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.44,0:10:38.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终结局将会如何发展呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:40.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请大家声援他们！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 下一问
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.41,0:10:46.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.25,0:10:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,球体表面积的计算公式是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.63,0:10:53.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,４πｒ²
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:56.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 好快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.55,0:11:00.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题还没念完呢 没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.34,0:11:05.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么清水同学 请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3/4πｒ³
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.36,0:11:22.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答对了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:30.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,球体表面积的计算公式是４πｒ²
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.12,0:11:34.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么球体体积的计算公式是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.88,0:11:38.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答案是3/4πｒ³ 非常精彩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.34,0:11:40.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来 清水同学离优胜也只差最后一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:43.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三位同学拿到6分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.93,0:11:46.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相当紧张刺激的平手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.39,0:11:47.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后藤同学也请加油
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.98,0:11:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 下一问
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.56,0:11:53.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:59.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神山高中学生会长的全名
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.07,0:12:02.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:06.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 清水同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陆山宗芳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:16.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别卖关子了行不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.29,0:12:18.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答对了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 福部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.39,0:12:26.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 我们都好遗憾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.43,0:12:29.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 居然平手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.06,0:12:32.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.02,0:12:35.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着说围棋部的趣事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.85,0:12:37.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棋子被偷走了几颗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:41.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 不是丢了而是被偷了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.15,0:12:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好笑的是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.03,0:12:46.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还收到了「围棋部的棋子我拿走了」的犯罪声明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.07,0:12:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟不会全都用到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.28,0:12:51.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以明明拿走十颗也没人会发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:54.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷那种东西做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:57.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那自然是玩五子棋之类了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.21,0:13:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看是其他部员的恶作剧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.30,0:13:03.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:05.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平手实在不过瘾 来分个高下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.76,0:13:10.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你接下来要参加什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.93,0:13:14.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天料理研的活动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK 这场比赛的胜负就留到那里去分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.94,0:13:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很期待哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:26.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不知趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.11,0:13:27.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}清水同学 你现在的心情如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:30.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对和谷同学比试没兴趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.33,0:13:33.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道奉太郎有没有认真看店呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.72,0:13:54.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有开张吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.35,0:13:58.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开 开着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.94,0:14:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写着KANYA祭由来的就是这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:02.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以翻翻看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:03.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.28,0:14:05.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,200日元而已 买回去看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:08.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,印得太多我们都要哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.62,0:14:14.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长 你石门水库没关
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.04,0:14:22.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 破掉了 麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.93,0:14:32.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请用这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:36.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 真亏你有这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.93,0:14:37.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.65,0:14:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是谢礼 给你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.57,0:14:46.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,气枪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.69,0:14:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是水枪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.74,0:14:54.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,园艺部在烤白薯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.99,0:14:57.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灭火要是拿水桶就太没意思了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.83,0:14:59.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那这个你们不是需要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:01.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是辅助兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:05.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主武器是这个 AK的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.88,0:15:07.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.13,0:15:09.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我走啦 谢喽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:15.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格洛克17吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:15.51,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,注：奥地利格洛克公司设计生产的第一枝手枪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.01,0:15:19.02,inter,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs150\pos(1100,178)\blur2}秋 分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.01,0:15:19.02,inter,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(472,342)\blur2}昼夜等长日 乃是秋分时
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.06,0:15:24.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到底 这本文集就很失败
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.23,0:15:26.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本就没人来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:31.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是趁现在画张海报吸引客人比较好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:38.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 是大家决定用这种风格的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.17,0:15:46.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要看我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.88,0:15:49.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一百部漫画的评论什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.09,0:15:52.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种死板的东西谁要看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.51,0:15:55.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 河内同学 少说两句吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.05,0:15:58.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到底 评论什么的根本没意义
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.27,0:16:00.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.35,0:16:02.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.66,0:16:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿福会相信我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.24,0:16:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是真的不想惹事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.71,0:16:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用是什么意思 学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.38,0:16:32.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一言以蔽之 就是读者的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.01,0:16:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,读者？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.47,0:16:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.72,0:16:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有漫画的趣味性原本就是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:49.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是谁画的都一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:50.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:54.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 有趣与否的区别体现在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.66,0:16:58.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不明白吗 伊原
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:00.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就在于读者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:06.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到底 就是取决于读者对趣味性的敏感度而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.71,0:17:16.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 敏感度低的人无法体会到趣味性吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:17.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.18,0:17:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才说评论是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.27,0:17:26.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只要读自己喜欢的作品 哈哈大笑就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.23,0:17:28.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的漫画都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:31.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种观点我绝对无法接受
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.40,0:17:33.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不会认输
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.32,0:17:35.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.61,0:17:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照你的逻辑 所谓的名作也是不存在的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.66,0:17:41.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名作当然是存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.49,0:17:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,定义呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.58,0:17:51.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长年累月经过众多读者筛选而留存下来的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.55,0:17:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是名作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.42,0:17:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你错了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:18:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名作一诞生就是名作了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种没经过时间考验的东西…你这才叫主观吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.77,0:18:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你错了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:07.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里错了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:09.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是经验问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.90,0:18:14.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐你只是没看到过让你怦然心动 觉得很了不起的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.53,0:18:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.49,0:18:19.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真敢说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:23.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作者的才能和技巧之差绝对是存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.62,0:18:33.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐 去年在这所学校的文化祭上出售的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.75,0:18:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名叫「傍晚便成骸」的漫画 你看过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.01,0:18:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:47.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我明天带来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.64,0:18:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那样你还不能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.85,0:18:51.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无话可说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.73,0:18:56.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来 代售「冰菓」的事就彻底说不出口了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:18:59.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.99,0:19:01.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:14.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fs45\c&H131517&\3c&HBAC0C2&\frz270\pos(1305,660)}不可错过! 正在决战中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:14.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fs45\c&H131517&\3c&HBAC0C2&\frz270\pos(1122,648)}少女之战in漫研
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:14.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fs45\c&H131517&\frz270\pos(811.5,594)\3c&HC3C7C9&}漫画论激辩中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:14.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\fs45\c&H131517&\3c&HBAC0C2&\frz270\pos(516,648)}巫女VS双性体
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:14.38,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,注：伊原COS的角色在其原作中是双性
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:14.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少女之战…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:16.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.34,0:19:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.26,0:19:18.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.38,0:19:20.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:23.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天还会继续 请务必来参观
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.23,0:19:30.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.94,0:19:34.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的宣传多少派上点用场了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:19:35.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:37.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卖了14本
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.53,0:19:38.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:41.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的宣传好像意外地有效
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.24,0:19:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头一炮算是打得很不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.91,0:19:45.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天再努力一把吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.24,0:19:48.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,料理竞赛我还是有自信的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.58,0:19:51.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个三人一组的比赛？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.79,0:19:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 三人一组？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.75,0:19:55.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.80,0:20:00.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为总务委员 却没把活动情况掌握清楚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.13,0:20:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.93,0:20:08.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,增加摊点和让墙报部报道我们 我都没办到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.31,0:20:10.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别介意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:16.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 有件事我很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.57,0:20:17.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很在意？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:26.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 还是…不在意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.58,0:20:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.87,0:20:31.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧 没写三人一组啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.25,0:20:36.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是三人一组 我听到料理研的人这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.33,0:20:38.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 失算了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.05,0:20:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为可以一个人出战的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.97,0:20:43.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说来 摩耶花
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.38,0:20:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漫研怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.18,0:20:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.77,0:20:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摩耶花 千反田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.19,0:20:57.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能陪我一起参加料理研的竞赛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.94,0:21:06.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是可以跟部长商量 请她让我中途离开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.91,0:21:09.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能起到宣传效果 我也想参加
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.49,0:21:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 总之凑到人了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.54,0:21:13.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是有多想参加啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.54,0:21:16.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对料理还是有点自信的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.13,0:21:19.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么好玩的大赛怎么能不去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.84,0:21:29.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}全校同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.89,0:21:32.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}以及前来参观的游客请注意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.18,0:21:34.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}本广播宣布
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.31,0:21:38.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}KANYA祭第一天的日程到此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.07,0:21:41.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}还留在校内的同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.02,0:21:42.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 折木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.86,0:21:45.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个 难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.73,0:21:47.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}请尽快关好门窗 离开学校
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.90,0:21:47.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 不…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.20,0:21:51.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.26,0:22:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.72,0:22:11.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.60,0:22:14.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.28,0:23:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用这个代替吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.53,0:23:09.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.37,0:23:54.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.24,0:23:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.58,0:24:00.54,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3\fs48\pos(722,890)}欢迎来到KANYA祭！
